<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Site Unavailable</title>
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: #064e3b;
        font-family: sans-serif;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: #d4af37; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      p { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #d1fae5; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <h1>This website is currently unavailable</h1>
      <p>This site has been suspended pending outstanding payment.</p>
      <p>To restore this website please contact the developer.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>